# Petrovka, Balyklinsky Selsoviet, Fyodorovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Petrovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Balyklinsky Selsoviet, Fyodorovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 32 as of 2010.
Geography
It is located 12&nbsp;km from Fyodorovka, 3&nbsp;km from Balykly.
